OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank bolsters plan to calm 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmarket turmoil             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England has announced new  
OL,6, measures aimed at ensuring an "orderly 
OL,7, end" to its emergency bond buying      
OL,8, scheme, which it brought in when some  
OL,9, pension funds were at risk of collapse.
OL,11,FThe Bank says that it will now buy up  
OL,12,Fto #10bn of government bonds a day,    
OL,13,Fdouble the previous limit of #5bn.     
OL,15,FSo far the Bank has bought only around 
OL,16,F#5bn bonds under the #65bn programme.  
OL,18,FThe scheme was introduced after the    
OL,19,Fgovernment's mini-budget sparked       
OL,20,Fturmoil on financial markets.          
